{"type":"message","id":"b23b6c83","parentId":"a2ec03ca","timestamp":"2026-04-02T06:40:36.836Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to optimize a \"TTS 选品大师 agent\" (TikTok Shop product selection master agent) based on this document. Let me think about what this means.\n\nLooking at the document, it's a comprehensive product selection strategy for hair accessories on TikTok Shop in Thailand and Vietnam. The document mentions:\n- A multi-agent system (选品 Agent、内容 Agent、运营 Agent、客服 Agent、供应链 Agent)\n- The creator is \"HALEI 的 OpenClaw\" and it's maintained by \"选品 Agent 团队\"\n\nThe user likely wants me to create or optimize an agent that specializes in this TikTok hair accessories product selection work. This would involve creating a dedicated agent with specific instructions based on this document.\n\nLet me think about what optimization would involve:\n1. The current workspace has AGENTS.md, SOUL.md, etc.\n2. There's already a SOUL.md that says the agent is a \"大总管\" (chief assistant) who coordinates sub-agents\n3. The document mentions various sub-agents like 选品 Agent, 内容 Agent, 运营 Agent, etc.\n\nSo the user probably wants me to:\n1. Create a specialized \"TikTok 选品大师\" agent specifically optimized for hair accessories product selection in Thailand/Vietnam markets\n2. This would be a sub-agent that can be spawned when needed\n\nLooking at the skills available, there's a \"飞书多 Agent 配置助手\" skill that says \"交互式引导配置多 Agent 系统，支持批量创建、凭证验证、角色模板\"\n\n\nI should check if there's already a product selection agent configured in the system, and review the workspace files to understand the current agent setup before proposing optimizations.","thinkingSignature":"c8fef22883bc1ad9b5af172c0433b5b3f257b11d08604763db37b05ebd57858e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dn3l2ka83ozg_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"kinds":["subagent"],"limit":10,"messageLimit":2}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model"