{"type":"message","id":"b65273f6","parentId":"bea3de4a","timestamp":"2026-04-02T06:40:58.508Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture. There are several sub-agents already created:\n1. `product-selector` - for product selection\n2. `数据分析专家` - data analysis expert\n3. `tts_hair_scout_agent` - TikTok hair scout agent\n4. And another one\n\nThe document mentions a multi-agent system with:\n- 选品 Agent (product selection)\n- 内容 Agent (content)\n- 运营 Agent (operations)\n- 客服 Agent (customer service)\n- 供应链 Agent (supply chain)\n\nThe user wants to optimize the \"TTS 选品大师 agent\" based on the comprehensive strategy document I just read. This document is about hair accessories selection for TikTok Shop Thailand and Vietnam.\n\nI think the user wants me to update/optimize the existing `product-selector` or `tts_hair_scout_agent` or create a better version of the selection agent based on this new v2.0 document.\n\nLet me think about what \"优化\" (optimize) means here:\n1. The document is very comprehensive - it has detailed workflows, criteria, tables, etc.\n2. It seems like the existing agents might be earlier versions or not fully aligned with this document\n3. The user wants to update the agent's instructions/prompts to reflect the v2.0 strategy\n\nI should:\n1. Check if there are existing agent configuration files I can update\n2. Or create an optimized version of the selection agent\n\nLet me check the workspace for any agent configuration or skill files related to product selection.","thinkingSignature":"59fb2fa4de5cafe2af8edf7b31937a93278cd5ee0213d10a2435466ac62298af"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_apkxcugy0m1d_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace -type f -name \"*.md\" -o -name \"*.json\" | head -30 && echo \"---\" && ls -la /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":25267,"output