{"type":"message","id":"47d90fe6","parentId":"291fe538","timestamp":"2026-04-02T06:43:11.374Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to make the \"选品Agent\" (product selection agent) actually run through the workflow described in the document. Based on the session history, I can see there's already a `tts_hair_scout_agent` sub-agent that has been set up, along with other agents like `数据分析专家`.\n\nLooking at the session history:\n1. There's a `tts_hair_scout_agent` sub-agent that was spawned before\n2. There's also a `数据分析专家` sub-agent  \n3. There was a `product-selector` agent\n\nThe user wants me to get the product selection agent to actually run through the complete workflow. Let me think about what needs to be done:\n\n1. The document describes a workflow with:\n   - Data collection (TikTok Shop backend, InfluTalk, EchoTik, 1688)\n   - Screening with hard filters\n   - Profit calculation\n   - Recommendation grading (S/A/B/C)\n   - Output to Feishu Bitable\n\n2. The existing `tts_hair_scout_agent` was already created but may not be fully functional\n\n3. I need to check the current state of the agent configuration and make it run\n\nLet me think about the approach:\n1. First, I should check if there's a skill for the product selector agent\n2. Or spawn the agent to run the workflow\n3. Or create/update the agent configuration\n\nLooking at the skills available, there's a `feishu-bitable` skill and `feishu-calendar` skill etc. There's also a `coding-agent` skill that can be used for coding tasks.\n\nThe best approach would be to:\n1. Check the current agent/skill setup for product selection\n2. Spawn or trigger the agent to run the workflow\n3. Make sure it outputs to Feishu Bitable as described in the document\n\nLet me first check what agents and skills are configured by looking at the workspace.\n\nActually, I don't have easy exec access without approval. \n\nI can use sessions_list to see the current agents and their statuses, then spawn the product selection agent to execute the workflow. Since there's already a `tts_hair_scout_agent` configured, I should check if it's operational and spawn it to run through the selection process, ensuring it outputs results to Feishu Bitable as outlined in the document.","thinkingSignature":"a8b5f6f7b9c0fc1ff32c15f7e1d1322b7b59a111972677113d60f3d54b134241"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，我来把选品 Agent 的流程跑通！\n\n让我先看看当前有哪些相关 Agent 及其状态：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hosau72b88wo_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"limit":20,"messageLimit":3}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":133,"output":542,"cacheRead":48267,"cacheWrite":13948,"totalTokens":62890,"cost":{"input":0.0000399,"output":0.0006504,"cacheRead":0.0028960199999999996,"cacheWrite":0.0052305,"total":0.00881682}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775112172828,"responseId":"061d42ed0791c90328d13d89d1298e38"}}
