{"type":"message","id":"08a75f18","parentId":"4cd1e75f","timestamp":"2026-04-02T06:43:27.224Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the full picture. The system has several sub-agents:\n1. `tts_hair_scout_agent` (label) - TikTok hair scout agent\n2. `product-selector` - Was used for Bluetooth earphones analysis\n3. `数据分析专家` - Data analysis expert\n4. `tiktok_scout_agent` - TikTok scout agent\n5. Several others\n\nThe user wants me to make the product selection agent run through the workflow in the document. The workflow involves:\n1. Data collection from TikTok Shop, InfluTalk, EchoTik, 1688\n2. Filtering based on hard criteria\n3. Profit calculation\n4. S/A/B/C grading\n5. Output to Feishu Bitable\n\nLooking at the existing agents:\n- `tts_hair_scout_agent` seems closest but was built for a different purpose (scouting TikTok videos for hair accessories)\n- The document describes a more comprehensive workflow\n\nI need to:\n1. Create a Feishu Bitable with the required fields (as per the document)\n2. Spawn a product selection agent that will run the workflow\n\nSince the document mentions the output should go to a Feishu Bitable, I should first create that Bitable, then spawn the agent to run the workflow.\n\nLet me start by:\n1. Creating the Feishu Bitable app and table with the fields specified in the document\n2. Then spawning a sub-agent to execute the product selection workflow\n\nThe fields required per the document:\n- 商品名称 (text)\n- 站点 (single select: 泰国/越南)\n- 三级类目 (single select: 发夹/发箍/发圈)\n- 售价（本地货币）(number)\n- 月销量 (number)\n- 增长率 (percentage)\n\n\n- 1688同款链接 (hyperlink)\n- 1688价格 (number, CNY)\n- 预估利润 (number)\n- 利润率 (percentage)\n- IP风险 (single select: 无/低/中/高)\n- 推荐等级 (single select: S/A/B/C)\n- 行动建议 (single select: 立即采购/观察/放弃)\n- 采集状态 (single select: 待采集/已采集/已上架)\n\nNow I'll create the Bitable with these fields, then spawn the agent to run the selection workflow.","thinkingSignature":"7c88892da598a1ebb6b5c168d2bed45ba81fb291ea7d62387c571bc4e9da211a"},{"type":"text","text":"看到系统里有几个相关 Agent，但之前都没能完整跑通流程。我来分步执行：\n\n**第一步：创建飞书多维表格**（承载选品数据）\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hdq1m16b75mg_1","name":"feishu_bitable_app","arguments":{"action":"create","name":"TTS发饰选品数据库 v2.0"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":43432,"output":574,"cacheRead":34951,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78957,"cost":{"input":0.013029599999999999,"output":0.0006887999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00209706,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01581546}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775112191737,"responseId":"061d4300df63380acb700fc5b2649e62"}}
