{"type":"message","id":"63fb120b","parentId":"bc863814","timestamp":"2026-04-02T06:48:43.608Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The exec command completed and showed the workspace structure. Now I can see the workspace has:\n- skills/ directory (10 items)\n- memory/ directory\n- Various config files\n\nI need to look at the skills directory to find the tiktok/hair related skills. Let me check the skills directory content using the already approved context.\n\nActually, the user already approved this command and it's the same command that just ran. The output shows the workspace structure. The exec finished successfully with code 0. I should now use the result to continue my task.\n\nI was trying to understand the current agent/skill setup. From the previous sessions_list output, I saw there were subagents like:\n- product-selector\n- tts_hair_scout_agent  \n- 数据分析专家\n- tiktok_scout_agent\n\nThese were spawned before but may not be fully functional. The user wants to get the selection agent workflow running.\n\nI had already created the Feishu Bitable table successfully. Now I need to figure out what's needed to run the actual TikTok product selection workflow.\n\nLet me check the skills directory to understand what agents/skills are available.\n\nFrom the output: \"10 halei halei 4096 4月 1 22:24 skills\" - this shows the skills directory has 10 items/directories. I need to explore this.\n\nActually wait - the previous exec command was already approved by the user and finished. I got the output showing the workspace structure. The system notification says \"An async command the user already approved has completed\" - this is just informing me the background command finished. I don't need to run it again.\n\nNow I should continue with my task. The key question is: how do I get the selection agent to actually run? \n\nThe user wants to \"把这流程让选品agent跑通\" - get the selection agent to run through the workflow.\n\nBased on what I know:\n1. There's a Feishu Bitable already created with the right fields\n\n\n2. The TikTok data sources (EchoTik/InfluTalk) aren't configured yet\n\nThe immediate path forward is to either demonstrate the workflow with sample data or set up browser-based automation through agent-browser to pull real TikTok content. I should ask the user which approach they prefer, or clarify what credentials they have available for the data sources.\n\nLooking back at the conversation flow, the user shared a document about TikTok Southeast Asian hair accessory selection strategy, asked me to optimize the TTS选品大师 agent based on it, then said they wanted to get the selection agent operational. I'd already started building out the Bitable table structure with the required fields and views from the document. Now I need to determine the next step for actually running the selection workflow.\n\nFrom what I can see in the workspace, there's a skills directory with configurations, and I recall earlier subagents like tiktok_scout_agent and tts_hair_scout_agent were created but didn't fully execute. The most practical approach now would be to either build a demonstration using realistic sample data to show how the complete selection workflow functions, or help the user set up the actual TikTok data integration if they have API credentials. I should ask which direction they want to pursue.","thinkingSignature":"f7756d9f019c1fe06a824f7311e08d95d99935b28a158969b950f2298a3eb2bd"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 好，workspace 扫描确认了现有结构。现在帮你把**选品 Agent 流程跑通**，分两条路走：\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 现在可以立刻跑通的两条路\n\n### 路线 A：「演示模式」— 用模拟数据跑完整流程 ✅ 马上能做\n\n我往刚建好的 Bitable 里**手动写入 5-10 个真实感样品**，覆盖不同等级（S/A/B/C），让你看到：\n- 硬性筛选怎么过滤\n- 利润怎么测算\n- 等级怎么判定\n- 结果如何在表格里呈现\n\n**你可以立刻看到效果**，后续有真实数据源直接替换即可。\n\n---\n\n### 路线 B：「自动化模式」— 对接真实数据源 ⏳ 需要配置\n\n需要以下任一数据源：\n| 数据源 | 用途 | 获取方式 |\n|--------|------|---------|\n| **EchoTok API** | 泰国/越南 TikTok 热销榜 | echotik.io 注册 |\n| **InfluTalk** | TikTok 创作者带货数据 | influTalk.io 注册 |\n| **1688 API** | 义乌采购价/供应商数据 | 阿里巴巴开放平台 |\n| **浏览器自动化** | 模拟人工抓取页面 | agent-browser（需配置）|\n\n---\n\n**你选哪条路？**\n- 选 **A**：我立刻演示，给你输出第一批样品数据\n- 选 **B**：告诉我你有哪个数据源的账号，我帮你对接\n\n另外，我也建议**先跑 A 验证流程，B 是后续规模化用的**，两者不冲突 🚀"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":983,"cacheRead":45272,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46255,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0.0011796,"cacheRead":0.00271632,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0038959199999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775112490627,"responseId":"061d442b95ecdf064c49d9660eb19f3c"}}
