4-02 14:45:08 GMT+8] Feishu[kiit] DM | ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb [msg:om_x100b53d4b686dca8c49d94d9bcca489]\\nSystem: [2026-04-02 14:45:12 GMT+8] Feishu[kiit] DM | ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb [msg:om_x100b53d4b7045cbcc2dc781bf5606ce]\\nSystem: [2026-04-02 14:45:13 GMT+8] Feishu[kiit] DM | ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb [msg:om_x100b53d4b3312cacc36740ab9287810]\\n\\n\\n\\n你看一下 系统后台又几个agent\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"timestamp\": 1775112587616,\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"3c3252d5\",\n            \"seq\": 72\n          },\n          \"senderLabel\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"The user is asking me to check how many agents are running in the system backend. Let me check the current sessions to see all agents.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n              \"id\": \"call_function_ypt3vdxr1jpk_1\",\n              \"name\": \"sessions_list\",\n              \"arguments\": {\n                \"limit\": 30,\n                \"messageLimit\": 2\n              }\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"minimax\",\n          \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 39,\n            \"output\": 66,\n            \"totalTokens\": 46253,\n            \"cacheRead\": 3555,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 42593,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0.016276575\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1775112587631,\n          \"responseId\": \"061d448cce812fc62ac8e87ebdb83aca\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"7ff89904\",\n            \"seq\": 73\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:subagent:64fffe46-20fa-4f40-8ed4-fe063e479320\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n      \"spawnedBy\": \"agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n      \"label\": \"product-selector\",\n      \"displayName\": \"feishu:g-agent-main-subagent-64fffe46-20fa-4f40-8ed4-fe063e479320\",\n      \"parentSessionKey\": \"agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"feishu\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1774612944071,\n      \"sessionId\": \"92009386-2680-4010-846f-e18b5821cd94\",\n      \"model\": \"openrouter/free\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 30661,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"done\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1774612665377,\n      \"endedAt\": 1774612852018,\n      \"runtimeMs\": 119548,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"feishu\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/home/halei/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/92009386-2680-4010-846f-e18b5821cd94.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"搜索功能完全不可用。我需要基于我的知识来给出评估。我会使用我已有的市场知识来分析中国蓝牙耳机的选品潜力。\\n\\n让我整理一个完整的评估报告。\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"由于网络搜索暂时不可用，我将基于行业知识和典型市场框架来为您快速评估中国蓝牙耳机的选品潜力。\\n\\n## 📊 中国市场蓝牙耳机选品潜力评估\\n\\n### 1. 市场规模与增长\\n- **市场成熟度**：中国是全球最大的TWS耳机市场，已进入成熟期但仍有增长空间\\n- **年销量**：预计2024-2025年保持5-10%的温和增长\\n- **渗透率**：智能手机用户渗透率约35-40%，仍有提升空间（对比欧美40-50%）\\n- **换机周期**：约2-3年，存量市场换机需求稳定\\n\\n### 2. 价格段分析（潜力排序）\\n\\n#### 🥇 **高潜力段：300-800元（中端主力）**\\n- **市场占比**：约50%的销量集中于此\\n- **特点**：性价比之王，功能全面（主动降噪、通透模式、低延迟）\\n- **竞争格局**：小米、OPPO、vivo、华为、QCY等激烈竞争\\n- **选品建议**：\\n  - 差异化功能（如空间音频、AI翻译）\\n  - 优秀音质+基础降噪\\n  - 续航能力>24小时\\n  - 多配色/联名款\\n\\n#### 🥈 **中潜力段：100-300元（入门性价比）**\\n- **市场占比**：约30%，增长稳定\\n- **特点**：学生、初购人群首选\\n- **选品建议**：\\n  - 基础功能可靠（连接稳定、续航达标）\\n  - 品牌认知度重要（华强北系风险高）\\n  - 突出单次续航或延迟优势\\n\\n#### 🥉 **低潜力段：800-2000元（中高端）**\\n- **市场占比**：约15%，利润率高\\n- **特点**：苹果、索尼、Bose垄断，华为强势\\n- **风险**：技术壁垒高，品牌粘性强\\n- **机会**：细分场景（运动、电竞、母婴）\\n\\n#### 🎯 **小众潜力：2000元以上（高端发烧）**\\n- **市场占比**：<5%，增量有限\\n- **适合**：声学背景深厚的品牌\\n\\n### 3. 产品形态机会点\\n\\n| 形态 | 现状 | 潜力 |\\n|------|------|------|\\n| **入耳式** | 主流（75%+） | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ |\\n| **半入耳** | 苹果引领，舒适度需求 | ⭐⭐⭐ |\\n| **头戴式** | 冬季/室内场景 | ⭐⭐ |\\n| **骨传导** | 运动细分，年增>20% | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ |\\n| **开放式（OWS）** | 新兴趋势，增长快 | ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ |\\n\\n### 4. 技术趋势与选品方向\\n\\n- **必选项**：蓝牙5.3+、低延迟模式、ENC通话降噪\\n- **加分项**：\\n  - 主动降噪（中端必备，通透模式）\\n  - 空间音频/头部追踪\\n  - AI功能（翻译、字幕、助听辅助）\\n  - 多设备连接（≥2台）\\n  - 无线充电\\n- **续航基准**：单次6h+，总续航24h+（降噪开）\\n\\n### 5. 渠道与营销洞察\\n\\n- **线上为主**：京东自营、天猫旗舰、抖音直播\\n- **新品策略**：首发期优惠+测评铺量+达人种草\\n- **内容营销**：开箱对比、音质测试、降噪场景\\n- **用户关注点排序**：续航 > 音质 > 降噪 > 舒适度 > 颜值\\n\\n### 6. 风险与建议\\n\\n#### ⚠️ **主要风险**\\n1. **同质化严重**：方案商成熟导致产品相似度高\\n2. **价格战激烈**：中低端利润压缩至10-15%\\n3. **库存压力**：技术迭代快，滞销风险高\\n4. **品牌门槛**：新品牌破圈需要内容营销投入\\n\\n#### ✅ **选品行动建议**\\n\\n**短期策略（3-6个月）：**\\n1. 主推 **300-500元** TWS，配置：ANC + 蓝牙5.3 + 28h续航\\n2. 搭配 **骨传导运动耳机**（400-600元）切入细分\\n3. 设计差异化：女性化配色/国潮联名/电竞低延迟版本\\n\\n**长期策略：**\\n1. 建立音频调音能力，避免纯方案商同质化\\n2. 布局AI语音助手集成，构建生态壁垒\\n3. 关注 **OWS开放式耳机会**的快速起量机会\\n\\n### 7. 潜力指数评分（满分5⭐）\\n\\n| 价格段 | 潜力 | 利润率 | 竞争度 | 综合 |\\n|--------|------|--------|--------|------|\\n| 100-300元 | 3.5⭐ | 低 | 极高 | 3.0⭐ |\\n| 300-800元 | 4.5⭐ | 中 | 高 | 4.0⭐ |\\n| 800-1500元 | 3.0⭐ | 高 | 高 | 2.5⭐ |\\n| 骨传导 | 4.0⭐ | 中高 | 中 | 3.8⭐ |\\n| OWS开放式 | 4.5⭐ | 高 | 中低 | 4.2⭐ |\\n\\n---\\n\\n**结论**：最推荐切入 **300-800元中端TWS** 和 **开放式耳机** 两个方向，前者量大但竞争激烈需靠营销突围，后者增长快利润高但市场教育需投入。短期内建议先以中端TWS走量，同步布局开放式产品储备。\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n          \"provider\": \"openrouter\",\n          \"model\": \"openrouter/free\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 581,\n            \"output\": 1363,\n            \"totalTokens\": 32024,\n            \"cacheRead\": 30080,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 0,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1774612822770,\n          \"responseId\": \"gen-1774612829-OvI4L71lnAhzCFP9mcUD\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"30876919\",\n            \"seq\": 14\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:subagent:483330f7-5eed-4ed4-b358-561c214d3223\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n      \"spawnedBy\": \"agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n      \"label\": \"数据分析专家\",\n      \"displayName\": \"feishu:g-agent-main-subagent-483330f7-5eed-4ed4-b358-561c214d3223\",\n      \"parentSessionKey\": \"agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"feishu\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1774602189426,\n      \"sessionId\": \"8a6148f8-f067-4922-9663-21e7d5cefe58\",\n      \"model\": \"openrouter/free\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 51189,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"done\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1774601080046,\n      \"endedAt\": 1774602123576,\n      \"runtimeMs\": 52282,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"feishu\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/home/halei/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/8a6148f8-f067-4922-9663-21e7d5cefe58.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [],\n          \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n          \"provider\": \"openrouter\",\n          \"model\": \"openrouter/free\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 0,\n            \"output\": 0,\n            \"totalTokens\": 0,\n            \"cacheRead\": 0,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 0,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"error\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1774602056903,\n          \"errorMessage\": \"429 Provider returned error\\nmistralai/mistral-small-3.1-24b-instruct:free is temporarily rate-limited upstream. Please retry shortly, or add your own key to accumulate your rate limits: https://openrouter.ai/settings/integrations\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"f26d8199\",\n            \"seq\": 93\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"Excellent! agent-browser is working! It can open example.com and take a snapshot. So the browser dependency is fine; Chrome is installed and working. The earlier install errors were just about missing some libraries (maybe not critical) and network fetch for Chrome itself (not needed since Chrome exists).\\n\\nSo the tts_hair_scout agent should be able to run. The issue is likely:\\n- The subagent is not running/triggered\\n- Bitable configuration is placeholder\\n- Maybe the agent isn't registered correctly\\n\\nNow I need to help the user get the agent to run and produce data.\\n\\nAs a data analysis expert, I should:\\n1. Help set up the Bitable table (create app and table with appropriate fields)\\n2. Update the params file with correct Bitable tokens\\n3. Trigger the agent to run and verify results\\n4. Then analyze the data\\n\\nBut the user's immediate question is about why the agent doesn't show in dashboard. I should address that first and then propose to help with the data pipeline.\\n\\nLet me craft a response that:\\n- Explains that subagents aren't shown in dashboard (by design)\\n- Confirms that agent-browser is now installed and working\\n- Identifies that the Bitable placeholders need to be replaced with actual tokens\\n- Suggests next steps to create Bitable and get the agent running\\n- Offers to create the Bitable structure and analyze results\\n\\nI am a subagent for data analysis, so I can help with creating the Bitable table (using feishu_bitable_app and feishu_bitable_app_table tools) and later analyze the data. I'll need the user's confirmation to create resources in their Feishu account.\\n\\nLet me prepare to use the feishu_bitable_app tool to create a new Bitable app for the TikTok hair scouting results. But first I should understand what fields the agent outputs. Looking at index.ts, the results are:\\n\\n```ts\\nresults.push({ ...item, llmScore: score, netProfit, price, productCost });\\n```\\n\\nWhere `item` contains: title, videoUrl, views, commentSnippet.\\n\\nSo each record should have:\\n- Title (text)\\n- Video URL (hyperlink or attachment) - but the code stores videoUrl as a string, likely just the URL\\n- Views (number)\\n- Comment snippet (text)\\n- LLM score (number)\\n- Net profit (number)\\n- Price (number)\\n- Product cost (number)\\n\\nAlso maybe add a timestamp.\\n\\nI can create a Bitable with these fields. The user might want additional fields like category, status, etc.\\n\\nBut before I proceed, I should confirm with the user that they want me to create the Bitable and proceed with the analysis. Since this is a continuation from a previous interaction, maybe the main agent already had some discussion with the user. But I'm a subagent that was specifically spawned for data analysis. I should introduce myself and offer help.\\n\\nActually, reading the subagent context at the top: \\\"You are a subagent spawned by the main agent for a specific task. Your Role: You were created to handle: 数据分析专家，擅长市场数据统计、销售趋势分析、竞品数据对比、可视化报表生成. Complete this task.\\\"\\n\\nSo the main agent spawned me to handle data analysis. The main agent likely dealt with the infrastructure setup and now it's my turn to work on the data side. That makes sense: they built the agent, now need to set up the data pipeline and analysis.\\n\\nThus, I should:\\n1. Acknowledge that the previous steps (skill creation, agent-browser install) are done or can be completed.\\n2. Focus on creating the Bitable table for results storage.\\n3. Provide a way to trigger the agent.\\n4. Once data is collected, perform analysis.\\n\\nLet me respond to the user's last message about not seeing the agent in the dashboard. I'll explain the situation, confirm that agent-browser is now installed, and then ask if they want me to create the Bitable table and run the analysis.\\n\\nActually, the user's latest message: \\\"什么情况呢， 为啥没有看到那个agent出现， 后台页面18789端口的web页面，只看一个main agent\\\" - they're asking what's going on and why they don't see the agent.\\n\\nI should answer that directly, then suggest concrete steps.\\n\\nAlso, note that there was an earlier message: \\\"测试重启完了吗，\\\" which the main agent already responded to. So the user might have received that response. Now they're following up.\\n\\nGiven I'm the subagent now, I need to take over. I should respond as the data analysis expert, acknowledging the situation and offering to proceed.\\n\\nBut the instructions: \\\"Continue where you left off. The previous model attempt failed or timed out.\\\" This suggests that the previous assistant (main agent) timed out or failed while trying to respond. My job is to complete that task. So I should effectively provide a response that the main agent was trying to craft, but now from the perspective of the subagent that's been spawned for data analysis.\\n\\nI think the most helpful thing is to provide a clear diagnosis and solution, then move to the data analysis setup.\\n\\nHere's my plan for the response:\\n\\n1. **Explain dashboard visibility**: Subagents are isolated and don't appear in the main dashboard by design. That's normal.\\n2. **Check agent status**: Use CLI commands to verify registration (but the sessions list hangs, maybe due to many sessions). I can suggest alternative: check the skill directory and ensure the agent can be triggered.\\n3. **Installation fix**: I've confirmed agent-browser is now installed. Chrome is available. So the agent can run.\\n4. **Bitable configuration**: The params file contains placeholders. We need to create a Bitable table and get its app_token and table_id. I can offer to create it.\\n5. **Trigger the agent**: Once Bitable is ready, we can manually trigger the agent to run once for testing, or wait for the cron.\\n6. **Analysis**: After data is collected, I'll generate statistics, trends, competitor comparisons, and visual reports.\\n\\nI'll ask the user for permission to create the Bitable, and also ask if they want to run the agent now or later.\\n\\nI can use the feishu_bitable_app tool to create the app, then create a table with appropriate fields.\\n\\nBut I need to be careful: the user might not have given explicit permission to create Bitable resources. I should ask first or state that I'm about to do it as part of the task.\\n\\nGiven that the main agent already told them \\\"已成功完成 TikTok 发饰选品 Agent 的搭建\\\" and the user is now asking follow-up, it's reasonable for me to proceed with the next logical steps: setting up the Bitable destination.\\n\\nI'll respond in Chinese since the user is speaking Chinese.\\n\\nLet me craft the response.\\n\\nFirst, I need to state who I am: I'm a data analysis subagent, continuing the work.\\n\\nI'll address the dashboard question.\\n\\nThen I'll propose: \\\"为了继续推进，我需要先创建飞书多维表格来存储选品结果。是否授权我创建表格？\\\" (To proceed, I need to create a Feishu Bitable to store the results. Do you authorize me to create the table?)\\n\\nIf they say yes, I'll proceed with creating the app and table. But in this context, I'm sending a message to the user. I can't wait for a response in this turn? Actually, I can ask and then wait for their reply. The instruction says I'm a subagent; my final response will be reported to the main agent/user. I can include a question and wait for them to reply in the same chat. That's okay.\\n\\nBut the conversation might continue. I'll ask for permission and also provide instructions they can follow if they prefer to do it themselves.\\n\\nAlternatively, I can just go ahead and create the table because the main agent already implied it was okay to set up. The user asked \\\"测试重启完了吗，\\\" and the main agent said everything is verified. The user then asked why they don't see the agent. So they're expecting the system to work. It's reasonable for me to complete the setup.\\n\\nGiven that the subagent is for data analysis, creating the Bitable is part of that pipeline. I'll do it.\\n\\nBut I need to be cautious: The Bitable app token and table ID need to be written back to the params file so the agent can use them. I'll also need to update the params file with the new tokens.\\n\\nSo steps:\\n1. Create Bitable app (maybe in the user's space)\\n2. Create a table named \\\"TikTok Hair Scout Results\\\" with the appropriate fields\\n3. Get the app_token and table_id from the creation response\\n4. Update /tmp/tts_hair_params.json with these tokens\\n5. Then maybe trigger a manual run to test\\n\\nBut I should also verify the skill code expects the params in that file. Yes, it reads from /tmp/tts_hair_params.json by default.\\n\\nLet's proceed.\\n\\nFirst, I'll use feishu_bitable_app create.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"我理解你的困惑。让我先梳理一下当前状态：\\n\\n## 📋 当前情况分析\\n\\n1. **Dashboard 不显示子 Agent 是正常的**  \\n   OpenClaw 的 Dashboard（18789 端口）默认只显示主会话（main agent）。子 Agent（如 `tts_hair_scout_agent`）运行在隔离会话中，不会出现在主会话列表里，除非它主动发送消息回主会话。这不是问题。\\n\\n2. **关键依赖已就绪**  \\n   我刚才检查并**安装了 `agent-browser`**，并且验证它可以正常工作（成功打开 example.com 并截图）。系统已自带 Google Chrome，浏览器自动化环境已经可用。\\n\\n3. **尚未生成结果的原因**  \\n   查看 `/tmp/tts_hair_params.json` 发现：\\n   ```json\\n   \\\"bitable_app_token\\\": \\\"PLACEHOLDER\\\",\\n   \\\"bitable_table_id\\\": \\\"PLACEHOLDER\\\"\\n   ```\\n   这两个参数还是占位符，说明**多维表格尚未创建**。子 Agent 即使运行，也无法写入结果。\\n\\n4. **子 Agent 是否在运行**  \\n   子 Agent 是由主 Agent 按需触发或按定时任务运行的。它平时不会常驻进程，而是在触发时启动、完成后退出。因此 `ps` 看不到进程是正常的。\\n\\n## 🎯 下一步：我需要你授权我来完成数据管道搭建\\n\\n作为数据分析专家，我现在可以：\\n\\n### ✅ 创建飞书多维表格（Bitable）用于存储选品结果\\n我会创建一个包含以下字段的表格：\\n\\n| 字段名 | 类型 | 说明 |\\n|--------|------|------|\\n| 标题 | 文本 | 视频标题 |\\n| 视频链接 | 超链接 | TikTok 视频 URL |\\n| 播放量 | 数字 | 视频播放数 |\\n| 评论摘录 | 文本 | 包含购买意向的评论 |\\n| LLM 评分 | 数字 | 0-100 的选品评分 |\\n| 净利润 | 数字 | 预估利润（美元） |\\n| 售价 | 数字 | 预估售价 |\\n| 成本 | 数字 | 预估成本 |\\n| 抓取时间 | 日期 | 记录创建时间 |\\n\\n创建后，我会：\\n1. 将新生成的 `app_token` 和 `table_id` 写入 `/tmp/tts_hair_params.json`\\n2. 手动触发一次子 Agent 运行，验证数据抓取、评分、写入全流程\\n3. 抓取完成后，对数据进行统计分析，生成可视化报表（趋势、品类分布、评分分布等）\\n\\n### 📍 现在需要你确认：\\n\\n**是否授权我在你的飞书空间中创建这个多维表格？**  \\n如果同意，我将立即开始创建表格并更新配置，然后触发一次测试运行。完成后我会生成分析报告。\\n\\n如果希望先检查或自定义表格字段，也可以告诉我你的需求。\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n          \"provider\": \"openrouter\",\n          \"model\": \"openrouter/free\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 501,\n            \"output\": 4794,\n            \"totalTokens\": 55983,\n            \"cacheRead\": 50688,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 0,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1774602071301,\n          \"responseId\": \"gen-1774602082-2BssLbf5RfVYhWCMRgI1\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"35bbf633\",\n            \"seq\": 94\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:subagent:35a36f61-da3b-46a3-b991-11d1531df526\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n      \"spawnedBy\": \"agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n      \"displayName\": \"feishu:g-agent-main-subagent-35a36f61-da3b-46a3-b991-11d1531df526\",\n      \"parentSessionKey\": \"agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"feishu\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1774598867204,\n      \"sessionId\": \"16839ad6-d23d-42a3-b8c5-7b0502d570ec\",\n      \"model\": \"openrouter/free\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,