 消费者需求热度\\n   - 其他（请说明）\\n\\n4. **预算与资源**：大概的采购/启动预算范围？\\n\\n请提供这些信息，我将立即开始市场调研和产品筛选，快速给您呈现潜在爆款清单。\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n          \"provider\": \"openrouter\",\n          \"model\": \"openrouter/free\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 25492,\n            \"output\": 949,\n            \"totalTokens\": 30921,\n            \"cacheRead\": 4480,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 0,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1774598843515,\n          \"responseId\": \"gen-1774598850-6EGFv5vcycc2WSnjwQbZ\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"9e74d719\",\n            \"seq\": 4\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:subagent:db04fc71-d290-400e-b807-11ab63f53934\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n      \"origin\": {\n        \"provider\": \"webchat\"\n      },\n      \"spawnedBy\": \"agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n      \"label\": \"tts_hair_scout_agent\",\n      \"displayName\": \"feishu:g-agent-main-subagent-db04fc71-d290-400e-b807-11ab63f53934\",\n      \"parentSessionKey\": \"agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"feishu\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1774596059905,\n      \"sessionId\": \"72054f66-fa51-42ec-8ac5-c74ac0937f6f\",\n      \"model\": \"openrouter/free\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 41826,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"done\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1774593691537,\n      \"endedAt\": 1774593760988,\n      \"runtimeMs\": 66888,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"feishu\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/home/halei/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/72054f66-fa51-42ec-8ac5-c74ac0937f6f.jsonl\",\n      