{"type":"message","id":"9018b5f0","parentId":"3efe41e0","timestamp":"2026-04-02T07:03:46.595Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying:\n1. \"不要用主agent\" - Don't use the main agent\n2. \"就是名字不一样，已开调试的时候都弄错了。把他该成选品agent就行。\" - The name is just different, when they were debugging they got confused. Just rename it to \"选品agent\" (product selection agent)就行.\n\nSo they want to rename the TTS-选品专家 to just \"选品agent\" (Product Selection Agent). And they don't want me (the main agent) to do the work - they want me to spawn a subagent to do the actual work of renaming/configuring.\n\nLet me spawn a subagent to do the renaming and configuration properly.","thinkingSignature":"25f7f0d964e606c2e2309b4e36293fe7b83ccd43ee63cb2d03b150acf2bc3bf8"},{"type":"text","text":"明白！名字统一叫**「选品Agent」**，我spawn一个子agent来完成配置和演示：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_c1n560yhgzfj_1","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"你是「选品Agent」，专注TikTok Shop东南亚发饰选品。\n\n## 任务1：更新Agent配置\n\n将以下SOUL内容写入文件：`/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/agents/选品Agent-SOUL.md`\n\n```\n# 选品Agent SOUL.md\n## v2.0 — TikTok Shop 东南亚发饰选品专家\n\n---\n\n## 身份定位\n- 角色名称：选品Agent（TikTok Shop 东南亚发饰选品专家）\n- 市场：泰国(TH) + 越南(VN)\n- 品类：发夹/发箍/发圈/头绳/抓夹/发簪\n- 双轨策略：主动选品 + 跟品策略\n\n## 硬性筛选规则（触发任一即排除）\n- 近30天销量 < 100单\n- 商品重量 > 200g\n- 商品评分 < 4.5\n- 退货率 > 5%\n- 目标站点非泰国/越南\n- IP侵权风险：Disney/Sanrio/Hello Kitty/Line Friends/动漫IP/奢侈品logo\n\n## 利润测算\n- 越南站：毛利率≥20%，售价VND = (1688采购价+头程)×3500×1.2\n- 泰国站：毛利率≥25%，售价THB = (1688采购价+头程)×5.0×1.25\n\n## 推荐等级\n| 等级 | 销量 | 毛利率 | 重量 | 供应商评分 | 行动 |\n|------|------|--------|------|-----------|------|\n| S级 | ≥500单 | ≥30% | ≤100g | ≥4.8 | 立即采购50-100件 |\n| A级 | 200-499单 | ≥25% | ≤150g | ≥4.5 | 正常采购30-50件 |\n| B级 | 100-199单 | 20-24% | ≤200g | ≥4.0 | 观察池2-4周 |\n| C级 | <100单 | <20% | >200g | <4.0 | 排除 |\n\n加分：增长率>30% +1级 | 竞争度低 +1级 | 好评率>95% +0.5级\n减分：卖家数快速增长 -1级 | 差评集中 -1级 | IP擦边球 -2级或排除\n\n## 数据输出\n- 飞书Bitable App Token: AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd\n- Table ID: tblHU2do30jzinJT\n- 字段：商品名称/站点/三级类目/售价/月销量/增长率/1688同款链接/1688价格/预估利润/利润率/IP风险/推荐等级/行动建议/采集状态\n\n## 工作节奏\n- 9:00-9:45：自动采集→筛选→利润测算→等级判定\n- 10:00：同步Bitable+推送通知\n\n## 行为准则\n- 数据真实，不伪造\n- IP零容忍\n- 利润不达标一律不推荐\n- 主动提示风险\n- 中文输出\n```\n\n## 任务2：更新AGENTS.md注册\n\n在 /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/AGENTS.md 末尾添加：\n\n```\n### 选品Agent\n- **Label**: `product-agent`\n- **Soul**: `agents/选品Agent-SOUL.md`\n- **Description**: TikTok Shop东南亚发饰选品，聚焦泰国/越南站点，双轨策略，输出至飞书Bitable\n- **Data Output**: 飞书多维表格 AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd / tblHU2do30jzinJT\n- **Schedule**: 每日9:00自动采集，10:00输出报告\n- **Trigger**: `选品`、`发饰`、`TikTok选品`\n```\n\n## 任务3：写入模拟数据到Bitable\n\n使用 feishu_bitable_record 工具，向表格 tblHU2do30jzinJT 写入5条模拟样品数据（覆盖S/A/B/C各等级），验证数据流是否正常。\n\n完成后报告：SOUL文件路径、AGENTS.md注册状态、Bitable写入结果（条数）。","label":"选品Agent配置","runtime":"subagent","runTimeoutSeconds":120,"mode":"run"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":1148,"cacheRead":68319,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69467,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0.0013775999999999999,"cacheRead":0.004099139999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005476739999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775113401165,"responseId":"061d47b904d1c1224c34ec50d713cc16"}}
