{"type":"message","id":"bce28fe8","parentId":"bdabf2be","timestamp":"2026-04-02T08:21:38.405Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-02 16:20:33 GMT+8] Feishu[kiit] DM | ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb [msg:om_x100b53d622371c88c2221e9d31a9c3d]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b53d622371c88c2221e9d31a9c3d\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-04-02 16:20 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```\n\n我知道你为啥找不到他了\n从配置看，子 agent 不是静态配置的，而是通过 sessions_spawn 工具动态创建的。\n从 subagents/runs.json 可以看到，子 agent 是这样启动的：\n\"spawnMode\": \"run\",\n\"label\": \"product-selector\",\n\"model\": \"openrouter/auto\",\n\"workspaceDir\": \"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace\"\n问题可能是：\n1. product-selector 目录在 agents/main/ 下，但没有在 agents.list 中注册为独立 agent\n2. 子 agent 是动态 spawn 的，不是通过目录发现的\n解决方案：\n如果你想让 product-selector 作为独立 agent 被发现，需要在 agents.list 中添加：\n{\n  \"id\": \"product-selector\",\n  \"name\": \"选品专家\",\n  \"agentDir\": \"/home/halei/.openclaw/agents/main/product-selector\"\n}\n或者，如果你想让它作为子 agent 使用，直接通过 sessions_spawn 工具调用即可，不需要在 agents.list 中注册。"}],"timestamp":1775118098315}}
{"type":"message","id":"17d1a57d","parentId":"bce28fe8","timestamp":"2026-04-02T08:22:02.058Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is explaining why I couldn't find the \"product-selector\" agent - it was dynamically spawned via sessions_spawn, not statically configured. They're telling me the architecture works like this:\n\n1. Sub-agents are dynamically created via `sessions_spawn`, not discovered from directories\n2. The `agents.list` or similar registry would have entries like \"tts\" and \"main\"\n3. To make an agent discoverable, it needs to be registered in `agents.list`\n\nThe user seems to be explaining this to help me understand the system better. They seem to be providing this information proactively.\n\nI should acknowledge this understanding and thank them for the explanation. This helps me understand the OpenClaw architecture better - agents are either:\n1. Statically registered in agents.list (like \"main\" and \"tts\")\n2. Dynamically spawned via sessions_spawn\n\nThe \"product-selector\" was a dynamically spawned sub-agent, not a statically registered one. That's why I couldn't find it as a \"file\" to read.\n\nI should respond acknowledging this and ask if there's anything specific they want to do with this knowledge, or if they want to proceed with other tasks.","thinkingSignature":"f1c2c9731ffd5f9fba2f64d27a42acddfadf0328359b2ee72afd4d0ac2eaf74a"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>明白了，感谢你解释这个架构：\n\n**OpenClaw Agent 的两种形态：**\n1. **静态注册**（`agents.list`）— 像 `main`、`tts` 这种，可以直接被发现和调用\n2. **动态 spawn**（`sessions_spawn`）— 像 `product-selector` 这种，是运行时临时创建的子进程，不在 agents.list 里\n\n所以我之前找不到\"选品专家agent\"不是因为路径问题，而是它本身就是通过 spawn 动态生成的会话，不是静态注册的 agent。\n\n现在 `tts` agent（id=tts）是通过静态注册的可独立调用 agent，它的 workspace-selector 下已有完整的 SOUL/TOOLS/USER 配置。\n\n---\n\n了解了架构之后，接下来你要：\n1. 配置 `tts` 的 cron 定时任务（每日9点自动选品）？\n2. 对接数据源密钥（EchoTik/InfluTalk）？\n3. 其他？</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":39,"output":434,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":102423,"totalTokens":102896,"cost":{"input":0.0000117,"output":0.0005208,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.038408625,"total":0.038941125}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775118098325,"responseId":"061d5a13bd9d180ef638f88d819047c3"}}
