{"type":"message","id":"1cc59540","parentId":"cfc4ca40","timestamp":"2026-04-02T09:17:38.486Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The approval system is really annoying. Let me answer the user's question about the approval system first, and then ask for approval to run the clawhub search command.\n\nFor the approval system question:\n- The user can set `security: \"allow-always\"` in the exec tool call to bypass approvals\n- Or they can configure `ask: off` in the gateway config for certain hosts\n- Card-based interactions - this might refer to interactive message cards in Feishu/Lark. I can use the feishu channel rules skill to format messages as cards.\n\nLet me respond to the user about both topics.","thinkingSignature":"8feddd0a076f9d9d888bada21878de28e514c251f7fac83121b1d0242fc30454"},{"type":"text","text":"**2. 关于批准功能的问题：**\n\n有两种方式可以减少批准弹窗：\n\n**方式一：设置全局免批准（你自行承担风险）**\n在 `~/.openclaw/gateway.json` 或 workspace 配置里，给 exec 工具设置 `security: \"allow-always\"`，这样所有命令都不弹确认。但这个方式有安全风险，我不建议开启。\n\n**方式二：我调用时用 `ask: off` 参数**\n我在 spawn exec 时可以加 `ask: \"off\"` 参数，这样你机器上已审批过的同类命令不会再弹窗。要这样配置吗？\n\n**方式三：卡片式交互**\n飞书支持卡片消息格式，我可以在回复时用卡片样式展示信息，比纯文本更清晰。需要我配置成卡片模式吗？\n\n---\n\n先把 ClawHub 排行榜查完（需要你批准上面那个命令），查完再决定装哪些 skill。批准吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":97545,"output":310,"cacheRead":12265,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":110120,"cost":{"input":0.029263499999999998,"output":0.000372,"cacheRead":0.0007358999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0303714}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775121444394,"responseId":"061d67244b5f72d0e39a4a08dd8e30a3"}}
